Task: Extend MarkdownRenderer to auto-detect and render math expressions

Summary: Created MarkdownRenderer component and parse-math-segments utility
that splits markdown content by math delimiters and renders via KaTeX.

Files created:
- components/textbook/MarkdownRenderer.tsx — main component, splits content into segments
- lib/textbook/parse-math-segments.ts — utility to tokenize block/inline math
- __tests__/components/textbook/MarkdownRenderer.test.tsx — 13 tests covering all math notations and existing markdown

Why: Lesson content contains LaTeX math expressions that must render correctly.
Approach: No new npm packages — used string segmentation to extract math blocks
and render via existing MathBlock/MathInline components.
